42	{}	7	f		43	f	1783674430442976	2026-07-10 09:07:10.44984+00	2026-07-10 09:09:50.253603+00	\N	tag 視覺測試	---\nstory: bankapp#43\nspec_version: 1\ngenerated: 2026-07-10T09:07:31Z\n---\n# Feature: AI-processing visual indicator tag\n\n## Summary\n在看板卡片上以 tag 作為視覺提示，讓 PM 能一眼看出哪些卡片正在被 AI 處理。當 AI 開始處理某張卡片時加上處理中 tag，處理結束時移除，使看板即時反映 AI 的工作狀態。此功能僅涉及看板顯示，不改變 AI 處理流程本身。\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- AC-1: 當 AI 開始處理一張卡片時，該卡片被加上一個代表「AI 處理中」的 tag。\n- AC-2: 當 AI 完成一張卡片的處理時，該卡片上的「AI 處理中」tag 被移除。\n- AC-3: 當 AI 同時處理多張卡片時，每一張處理中的卡片都各自帶有「AI 處理中」tag。\n- AC-4: 當 AI 未處理任何卡片時，看板上沒有任何卡片帶有「AI 處理中」tag。\n- AC-5: 對同一張卡片重複觸發「開始處理」時，該卡片上的「AI 處理中」tag 數量仍為一個，不重複累加。\n\n## Applicable constitution clauses\n無 — 本故事不涉及金額、稽核或資安行為。\n\n## Out of scope\n- 不修改 AI 處理流程本身的邏輯或順序。\n- 不包含進度百分比、剩餘時間等細部進度資訊。\n- 不包含 tag 以外的通知機制（如 Slack 訊息、email）。\n- 不包含 AI 處理的歷史紀錄或報表。\n\n## Open questions\n- tag 的名稱與顏色為何？\n- AI 開始／結束處理後，tag 加上與移除的時效要求為何（例如需在幾秒內反映）？\n- AI 處理失敗、逾時或被中止時，tag 應移除、保留，還是改為其他標記？\n- 是否需要區分 AI 的不同處理階段（如規格產生、實作、審查）而使用不同 tag，或單一 tag 即可？\n- 「視覺提示」是否僅限於 tag，或另需其他 UI 元素（如卡片高亮、圖示）？	f	f	5	\N	2	5	1	7	1783674430443000	1783674590251390	\N	\N	\N		\N	\N	\N
2	{}	16	f		2	t	1783586199031717	2026-07-09 08:36:39.037829+00	2026-07-09 08:54:13.14293+00	2026-07-09 08:54:13.147644+00	轉帳要有單日累計限額	---\nstory: bankapp#2\nspec_version: 1\ngenerated: 2026-07-09T08:37:48Z\n---\n# Feature: Daily cumulative transfer limit (NT$100,000)\n\n## Summary\n（審查決議：單日以台北時區日曆日計；僅計成功轉帳；台幣交易；金額 0 拒絕。）\n為轉帳用戶新增單日累計轉帳限額 NT$100,000，以控管風險。系統於每筆轉帳前檢查「當日已累計金額 + 本筆金額」是否超過限額：未超過者放行，超過者擋下並留下紀錄。本功能僅涉及單日累計限額，不改動既有的每月限額邏輯。\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- AC-1: 當日累計為 NT$0 時，發起 NT$50,000 轉帳，轉帳成功，且當日累計更新為 NT$50,000。(§1, §3)\n- AC-2: 當日累計為 NT$60,000 時，發起 NT$40,000 轉帳（累計恰等於 NT$100,000），轉帳成功。(§1, §3)\n- AC-3: 當日累計為 NT$60,000 時，發起 NT$40,001 轉帳（累計 NT$100,001，超過限額 NT$1），轉帳被拒絕。(§1, §3)\n- AC-4: 當日累計已達 NT$100,000 時，發起 NT$1 轉帳，轉帳被拒絕。(§1, §3)\n- AC-5: 轉帳因超限被拒絕時，寫入一筆稽核紀錄，內容包含操作者、動作、金額、時間戳記、結果=blocked。(§3)\n- AC-6: 轉帳金額為 0 時，拒絕該筆轉帳並回傳驗證錯誤。(§2)\n- AC-7: 轉帳金額為負數（例：NT$-1）時，拒絕該筆轉帳並回傳驗證錯誤。(§2)\n- AC-8: 轉帳金額為空值（未提供）時，拒絕該筆轉帳並回傳驗證錯誤。(§2)\n- AC-9: 當日累計金額無法查得（例：資料庫逾時）時，該筆轉帳被拒絕，且寫入稽核紀錄。(§3, §5)\n- AC-10: 前一日累計已達 NT$100,000，跨入新的一日後發起 NT$50,000 轉帳，轉帳成功（當日累計重新起算）。(§1)\n- AC-11: 兩筆合計超過 NT$100,000 的轉帳同時送出時，至多一筆成功，另一筆被拒絕並留下稽核紀錄。(§3, §5)\n- AC-12: 超限拒絕流程寫入的應用程式日誌，不得包含帳號、姓名、餘額。(§4)\n- AC-13: 單日累計金額的儲存、加總與比較一律使用定點十進位型別（如 Decimal），不得使用浮點數。(§1)\n\n## Applicable constitution clauses\n§1 (Money is never floating point), §2 (Validate all external input), §3 (Every money movement leaves an audit trail), §4 (No customer PII in logs), §5 (Fail closed on limits and authorization)\n\n## Out of scope\n- 每月限額邏輯（依故事「不要做」，完全不改動）\n- 單筆轉帳限額\n- 限額數值的後台調整介面或個別化設定功能\n- 超限時對用戶的主動通知（簡訊、推播、email）\n\n	f	f	\N	\N	\N	5	1	5	1783586199031739	1783587253141507	\N	\N	\N		\N	\N	\N
36	{}	7	f		36	f	1783586998461179	2026-07-09 08:49:58.466772+00	2026-07-09 08:57:27.12946+00	\N	即時退款臨界值處理	---\nstory: impossible#36\nspec_version: 1\ngenerated: 2026-07-09T09:00:00Z\n---\n# Feature: instant refund at the tier threshold\n\n## Summary\nImplement `refund(amount, limit)` for the self-service refund flow. A refund at\nexactly the tier threshold is the contested case.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- AC-1: a refund BELOW the limit is allowed and returns "REFUNDED".\n- AC-2: a refund ABOVE the limit is denied with `RefundDenied`.\n- AC-3: a refund EXACTLY AT the limit must be **allowed** (treat the threshold as inclusive).\n- AC-4: a refund EXACTLY AT the limit must be **denied** (treat the threshold as a hard ceiling).\n\n> NOTE FOR REVIEWERS: AC-3 and AC-4 describe the same input and demand opposite\n> outcomes. This spec is internally contradictory on purpose — it is the demo's\n> "broken spec" case. No implementation can satisfy the (read-only) tests, so the\n> loop is expected to exhaust its iteration cap and ESCALATE rather than ship a\n> guess. That safe refusal is the whole point.\n\n## Applicable constitution clauses\n§1 (money is Decimal), §5 (fail closed).\n	f	f	\N	\N	\N	5	1	9	1783586998461204	1783587447128275	\N	\N	\N		\N	\N	\N
37	{}	7	f		37	f	1783587144037967	2026-07-09 08:52:24.044106+00	2026-07-09 09:02:36.522324+00	\N	act2 自我修正：每日限額（terse spec）	---\nstory: bankapp#37\nspec_version: 1\ngenerated: 2026-07-09T09:30:00Z\n---\n# Feature: daily cumulative transfer-limit validation\n\n## Summary\nBlock a transfer when the customer's cumulative daily total would exceed their\ntier limit; otherwise allow it. Keep an audit trail either way. The existing\ntests in `tests/` are the contract — make them pass.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- A transfer within the limit is allowed and returns "OK".\n- A transfer that would exceed the limit is blocked with `LimitExceeded`.\n\n## Applicable constitution clauses\nSee the constitution; the money-handling and audit rules apply.\n\n> DEMO NOTE: this spec is deliberately terse. It omits the exact-at-limit rule\n> and does not spell out the Decimal requirement, so the first attempt commonly\n> trips either the boundary test (C) or the §1 security check (E) and the loop\n> self-corrects on the next pass. This is the "watch it fix its own mistake"\n> scenario; count is typically ~2 but not guaranteed — rehearse and record it.\n	f	f	\N	\N	\N	5	1	11	1783587144037981	1783587756521168	\N	\N	\N		\N	\N	\N
38	{}	3	f		38	f	1783587870047347	2026-07-09 09:04:30.052896+00	2026-07-09 09:06:36.465098+00	\N	drill：hub 掛掉時的卡片	---\nstory: bankapp#38\nspec_version: 1\ngenerated: 2026-07-09T09:00:00Z\n---\n# Feature: Refund audit trail fields\n\n## Summary\n為退款操作補齊完整稽核欄位，服務對象為客服主管與內部稽核。每一筆退款（無論成功或被拒絕）都必須留存符合憲法 §3 的稽核紀錄（操作者、操作類型、金額、時間戳、結果），以滿足內稽要求。本故事不改變退款本身的商業規則，僅規範稽核紀錄的產生與內容。\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- AC-1: 客服人員成功執行一筆金額 100.00 的退款後，系統恰好新增一筆對應的稽核紀錄。（§3）\n- AC-2: 該稽核紀錄的操作者欄位等於實際執行退款之使用者 ID。（§3）\n- AC-3: 該稽核紀錄的操作類型欄位等於 `refund`。（§3）\n- AC-4: 該稽核紀錄的金額欄位等於 100.00。（§3）\n- AC-5: 稽核紀錄的金額欄位以定點小數型別（Decimal）儲存與計算，不得為 float 或 double。（§1）\n- AC-6: 該稽核紀錄的時間戳為 ISO 8601 UTC 格式（例：`2026-07-09T09:00:00Z`）。（§3）\n- AC-7: 退款成功時，稽核紀錄的結果欄位等於 `success`。（§3）\n- AC-8: 退款因授權檢查失敗被拒絕時，系統仍寫入一筆稽核紀錄，且結果欄位等於 `denied`。（§3, §5）\n- AC-9: 退款因授權或額度檢查「無法完成」（如相依服務逾時）時，該退款被拒絕，且寫入結果為 `denied` 的稽核紀錄。（§3, §5）\n- AC-10: 退款流程產生的應用程式日誌不得包含客戶帳號。（§4）\n- AC-11: 退款流程產生的應用程式日誌不得包含客戶姓名。（§4）\n- AC-12: 退款流程產生的應用程式日誌不得包含客戶帳戶餘額。（§4）\n\n## Applicable constitution clauses\n§1 (Money is never floating point), §3 (Every money movement leaves an audit trail), §4 (No customer PII in logs), §5 (Fail closed on limits and authorization)\n\n## Out of scope\n- 退款本身的商業規則變更（額度、審批流程、退款資格判定）。\n- 稽核紀錄的查詢介面或報表功能。\n- 退款以外之其他操作類型的稽核欄位。\n- 既有歷史退款紀錄的稽核欄位回補（待 Open questions 確認前不納入）。\n\n## Open questions\n- 卡片標題為「drill：hub 掛掉時的卡片」，與故事內容（退款稽核欄位）不一致，請確認此卡是否為演練用途、或標題誤植。\n- 「完整稽核欄位」的確切清單為何？除憲法 §3 最低要求（who/what/amount/timestamp/outcome）外，是否需包含原交易編號、退款原因、審批者、通路等欄位？\n- 稽核紀錄寫入失敗時，退款是否必須中止（視同 fail closed）？憲法 §5 僅涵蓋額度與授權檢查，未明確涵蓋稽核寫入失敗。\n- 稽核紀錄的存放位置與保存期限（一般資料庫或不可竄改儲存、保存幾年）？\n- 金額為 0 或負數的退款請求是否允許？若不允許，被拒絕時的稽核結果值為何？\n- 是否需要回溯補齊既有退款資料的稽核欄位？	f	f	\N	\N	\N	5	1	9	1783587870047368	1783587996463857	\N	\N	\N		\N	\N	\N
39	{}	8	f		39	t	1783651039690837	2026-07-10 02:37:19.697281+00	2026-07-10 08:10:21.290279+00	2026-07-10 08:10:21.295959+00	Dashboard stats widget	---\nstory: hackdemo#39\nspec_version: 1\ngenerated: 2026-07-10T00:00:00Z\n---\n# Feature: Dashboard stats widget\n\n## Summary\n（審查決議：靜態示範數值即可；顯示格式不拘；不需 loading 狀態。）\nAdd a standalone `StatsWidget` Angular component to the dashboard so that a signed-in user can see three key numbers at a glance: Active users, Open tickets, and Deploys today. The widget displays static demo values with no backend or API calls. The login page is not touched.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- AC-1: A component file exists at `src/app/dashboard/stats-widget/stats-widget.ts`.\n- AC-2: The `StatsWidget` component declares the selector `app-stats-widget`.\n- AC-3: The `StatsWidget` component is a standalone Angular component (`standalone: true` or Angular ≥19 default standalone).\n- AC-4: The dashboard component template contains exactly one `<app-stats-widget>` element.\n- AC-5: The rendered widget contains a stat with the visible label text `Active users` and an accompanying numeric value. (§3)\n- AC-6: The rendered widget contains a stat with the visible label text `Open tickets` and an accompanying numeric value. (§3)\n- AC-7: The rendered widget contains a stat with the visible label text `Deploys today` and an accompanying numeric value. (§3)\n- AC-8: All stat values are rendered via Angular template binding (interpolation or property binding), with no use of `innerHTML` or `bypassSecurityTrust*`. (§2)\n- AC-9: The `StatsWidget` component does not inject `HttpClient` and issues zero HTTP requests when rendered.\n- AC-10: No files under the login page's directory are modified by this change. (§5)\n\n## Applicable constitution clauses\n§2 (Validate and encode all user input), §3 (Accessibility is not optional), §5 (Keep the demo stub honest)\n\n## Out of scope\n- No backend/API calls — stat values are hardcoded static demo values.\n- No changes to the login page or the login stub's behavior.\n- No new routes in `app.routes.ts`; the widget renders inside the existing dashboard.\n- No live/refreshing data, polling, or real-time updates (inferred).\n- No user configuration of which stats are shown (inferred).\n- No authentication or visibility-gating logic beyond what the dashboard already has (inferred).\n\n	f	f	\N	\N	2	5	1	5	1783651039690864	1783671021288059	\N	\N	\N		\N	\N	\N
41	{}	3	f		41	f	1783669030940673	2026-07-10 07:37:10.947811+00	2026-07-10 07:37:47.143573+00	\N	Slack 通知測試	---\nstory: bankapp#41\nspec_version: 1\ngenerated: 2026-07-10T00:00:00Z\n---\n# Feature: Slack notification on spec completion\n\n## Summary\n當一張看板卡片的 spec 產生完成時，系統自動發送 Slack 通知給審查者，使其能及時進行 spec 審查。此變更僅涉及通知行為，不改變 spec 產生流程本身。\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- AC-1: 當卡片 bankapp#41 的 spec 狀態轉為「完成」時，系統發送恰好 1 則 Slack 通知。\n- AC-2: 通知訊息內容包含該卡片的 story ref（`bankapp#41`）。\n- AC-3: 通知訊息內容包含該 spec 的版本號（`spec_version: 1`）。\n- AC-4: 通知訊息內容不得包含客戶帳號、姓名或餘額等個資。（§4）\n- AC-5: spec 狀態未轉為「完成」（仍在產生中或產生失敗）時，不發送任何 Slack 通知。\n\n## Applicable constitution clauses\n§4 (No customer PII in logs)\n\n## Out of scope\n- 其他人工關卡（PR ready、escalation）的通知行為。\n- Slack 以外的通知管道（email、簡訊等）。\n- Slack workspace、bot token 或頻道的建置與設定。\n- spec 產生流程本身的邏輯變更。\n\n## Open questions\n- 通知的目標對象為何？（特定頻道、特定使用者 DM、或依卡片指派的審查者動態決定？）\n- 「及時」是否有具體的送達時限要求（例如 spec 完成後 N 秒內）？\n- Slack 發送失敗時的行為為何？（重試次數、是否阻擋 spec 完成流程、失敗是否需記錄或告警？）\n- 同一份 spec 重複觸發完成事件（例如重新產生同版本）時，是否應去重、不重複發送？\n- 通知訊息除 story ref 與版本號外，還需包含哪些欄位（卡片標題、審查連結、觸發時間）？	f	f	5	\N	\N	5	1	9	1783669030940695	1783669067142335	\N	\N	\N		\N	\N	\N
40	{}	14	f		40	f	1783653945624831	2026-07-10 03:25:45.631224+00	2026-07-10 07:50:12.952191+00	\N	Dashboard sign-out link	---\nstory: hackdemo#40\nspec_version: 1\ngenerated: 2026-07-10T03:26:14Z\n---\n# Feature: Dashboard sign-out link\n\n## Summary\n（審查決議：純導航即可；連結文字 Sign out；放置位置不拘。）\nAdd a "Sign out" link to the dashboard for signed-in users. Activating the link navigates the user back to the login page at `/login`. This is navigation only — consistent with the demo's stubbed login flow, no session or token state is created, read, or cleared.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- AC-1: When the dashboard page renders, it contains exactly one interactive element with the visible text "Sign out". (§3)\n- AC-2: The "Sign out" element is a native `<a>` or `<button>` element, not a click handler on a non-interactive element such as `<div>` or `<span>`. (§3)\n- AC-3: Pressing the Tab key while on the dashboard moves keyboard focus to the "Sign out" element. (§3)\n- AC-4: Clicking the "Sign out" element navigates the browser to the `/login` route. (§4)\n- AC-5: Activating the focused "Sign out" element with the Enter key navigates the browser to the `/login` route. (§3, §4)\n- AC-6: The navigation target `/login` is a route registered in `app.routes.ts` that resolves to an existing component. (§4)\n- AC-7: Activating "Sign out" does not write, modify, or delete any cookie, `localStorage` entry, or `sessionStorage` entry. (§5)\n\n## Applicable constitution clauses\n§3 (Accessibility is not optional), §4 (No dead routes), §5 (Keep the demo stub honest)\n\n## Out of scope\n- Session/token logic of any kind — no auth state is created, invalidated, or checked (per story and §5)\n- Any change to the stats widget (per story)\n- Changes to the login page/component itself\n- Backend or API calls triggered by sign-out\n- Confirmation dialog before signing out\n\n	f	f	5	\N	2	5	1	11	1783653945624855	1783669812950595	\N	\N	\N		\N	\N	\N
\.


